name: global-process-queue-js
description: With the Global Process Queue you can create a Queue of ASYNC and AWAIT Processes for your Node.JS System. This Package provides an API to create an Initializer and a Finisher Tasks to run before and after your Processes Queue be executed.
author: Maykonn Welington Candido <maykonn@outlook.com> (https://github.com/Maykonn)
